# Game APIs

### Create a game

POST {{HostAddress}}/games/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameType": "Game6x4",
  "playerName": "test"
}

### Set a move

@id = 50b38038-838e-404f-9bfd-7b87a0344b10

PATCH {{HostAddress}}/games/{{id}}
Content-Type: {{contenttype}}

{
  "gameType": "Game6x4",
  "playerName": "test",
  "moveNumber": 1,
  "guessPegs": [
    "Green",
    "Blue",
    "Red",
    "Yellow"
  ]
}

